               <p>I was present when the prisoner was taken; I saw him attempt to stab Mr. Caswell; I helped to take him.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>They threw brickbats at me, and used me very ill. I hope you will forgive me; it is the first offence I have been guilty of.</p>
